{{Short description|8th-century Buddhist monk and astronomer}} {{for multi|the Vietnamese monk with the same Chinese dharma name|Thích Nhất Hạnh|the city in [[:en:Jiangsu|Jiangsu]]|Yixing|the member of EXO|Lay (entertainer)}}
